Extract the package and run the prebuilt binaries:

  tar -xvzf Poker_V1.0.tar.gz
  cd Poker_V1.0

Start the server:

  cd bin
  ./poker_server

Then start a client in another terminal or on another machine:

  cd bin
  ./poker_client

The server uses port 10160 by default. In the client login screen, enter the
server hostname and port 10160.

This user package does not require compilation. If the host cannot open the GUI
server window, run `./poker_server_headless` instead.

For gameplay and connection instructions, see `doc/Poker_UserManual.pdf`.
